title: Midnight Cowboy Soundtrack (1969)
description:
There seem to be lots of people out there who&#039;d like this soundtrack, and I was looking for a decent copy myself. No luck! So I took my VERY scratched almost-40 year old album and processed it as best I could. Very happy with the results, although the high frequency stuff (cymbals etc.) is a bit lacking. In all though, an excellent result an I thought it should be shared!
